[<em>The Synodikon of the Sunday of Orthodoxy. Summary with
appendices</em>], Odessa: &#1058;&#1080;&#1087;.
&#1054;&#1076;&#1077;&#1089;&#1089;&#1082;&#1072;&#1075;&#1086;
&#1042;&#1086;&#1077;&#1085;&#1085;&#1072;&#1075;&#1086;
&#1054;&#1082;&#1088;&#1091;&#1075;&#1072;.</li>

<li>Walter, D., 2021, &ldquo;John Italos on authypostaton and
authyparkton in Quaestio 7 and his processing of Psellos&rsquo;s Phil.
min. I, Op. 7&rdquo;, in <em>The Byzantine Platonists,
284&ndash;1453</em>, F. Lauritzen and S. K. Wear (eds), Steubenville:
Franciscan University Press, 192&ndash;206.</li>
</ul>
